title: "RCE (Remote Component Environment)"
license: EPL-1.0
abstract: >
  This software is a distributed, workflow-driven integration environment.
  It is used by engineers and scientists to design and simulate complex 
  systems (e.g., aircraft, ships, or satellites) by using and integrating
  their own design and simulation tools.
